						<h2 class="slide-title">
							Bathroom and Wetroom re-fit or re-design are a speciality						</h2>
						<a class="post-edit-link" href="http://localhost:8888/mlplumbing/wp-admin/post.php?post=3358&#038;action=edit">Edit</a>					</div>
