<div id="tagline" class="tagline dark"><div class="container">M Luscombe Plumbing and Heating is a small family run service based near Truro, Cornwall, servicing all of Mid Cornwall. We are a husband and wife team who are known for our professionalism, reliability, honesty, efficiency, and quality workmanship all delivered with the highest possible customer service.

We are dedicated to providing our customers with honest service. You will never be met with surprises when you work with us. We keep our process straightforward and transparent so you know what to expect from start to finish.

You won't have to worry about further issues occurring after our job is done. We do not just provide surface repairs or carry out one-size-fits-all solutions. Our highly experienced engineer performs a thorough assessment of your system to locate the source of the problem. This allows us to provide the best solution.

We cover all aspects of oil fired central heating systems and plumbing works, full bathroom and wet room refurbishments are also a speciality.

Whether you require a boiler change, boiler repair, or a fully installed central heating system; a new basin, tap or complete bathroom refit we would be delighted to accommodate all of your requirements and find you a solution whatever your plumbing problem or project involves.

We do not recommend products or services that you do not need, nor do we surprise you with hidden charges.

For a no obligation quotation or advice call our office on 01872 262821 or 07833 452766</div></div><div id="contact" class="contact">
