	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content">
	<div id="bathrooms" class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-5f9c049220616 sectiontitle" data-node="5f9c049220616">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<h1 style="text-align: center;">Bathrooms</h1>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
	</div>
</div>
	</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="fl-row fl-row-fixed-width fl-row-bg-none fl-node-5f9c048bb25be" data-node="5f9c048bb25be">
	<div class="fl-row-content-wrap">
						<div class="fl-row-content fl-row-fixed-width fl-node-content">
		
<div class="fl-col-group fl-node-5f9c048bc1f8d" data-node="5f9c048bc1f8d">
			<div class="fl-col fl-node-5f9c048bc213e" data-node="5f9c048bc213e">
	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content">
	<div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-5f9c047e62a28" data-node="5f9c047e62a28">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<p>We would be delighted if you wanted to turn to us for all aspects of your new bathroom project; we will present you with options that best fit your particular needs.</p>
<p>All works can be organised or catered for from start to finish. Our engineer will consult with you about your requirements and discuss all options with you in the comfort of your home, ensuring that personalised solutions are offered that take your property's needs as well as your budget into account.</p>
<p>We can undertake works from start to finish including plumbing and wall or floor coverings. If you would like us to take the pressure away from you we can also arrange any trades required to work alongside us on your project.</p>
<p>From the best possible standard of bathrooms to walk in showers and wet rooms, let us dedicate our time to making your home perfect.</p>
<p>We will provide you with a no obligation estimate which is designed to give you an idea approximate cost, based on the ideas discussed at an initial consultation and maintaining a level of quality that is already present in your home. These costs will be by no means the only possible options you have and we would welcome the opportunity to discuss them with you further to ensure that we achieve your perfect bathroom.</p>
<p>We do not sell any specific suites so your options will be endless, you can take advantage of any offers we can find available to you at the time.</p>
<p>All of our estimates offer a detailed breakdown of costs to ensure transparency of service. Final costs can vary as it is not always possible to predict what will be found beneath and existing bathroom in terms of pipe work and drainage, but these areas will be discussed at all times with you from start to finish, ensuring that you know there will be no escalating costs.</p>
<p>Call us now on 01872 262821 for all your <a href="http://www.mlplumbingandheating.co.uk/plumbing.htm">plumbing</a> and <a href="http://www.mlplumbingandheating.co.uk/heating.htm">heating</a> needs, to be one step closer to your vision becoming your bathroom!</p>
</div>
